This directory contains files that provide support for code folding 
and syntax highlighting for editing Logtalk source files with the 
KDE Kate and KWrite text editors (http://kate.kde.org/).


To install copy the file "logtalk.xml" to the directory:

    $(KDEDIR)/share/apps/katepart/syntax/

or:
    
    ~/.kde/share/apps/katepart/syntax/

and restart Kate and KWrite.


THIS SYNTAX FILE IS UNDER DEVELOPMENT.
